{"tid":1835552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實戴唔戴口罩好？","createTime":"2020-01-23T01:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T07:58:58.000Z","uid":71060,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b094e532212f2e0e1a94f211257474e3734686","tid":1835552,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"一方面見到啲人叫藍絲小粉紅相信黨，唔好戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n另一方面有藍絲咳嗰陣又叫佢戴返個口罩，唔好周圍傳染人<br />\n<br />\n佢地啲腦咁細，咁矛盾嘅訊息量會唔會搞到佢地集體hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我都唔知叫唔叫我屋企啲廢老戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴，佢瀨嘢我都係咁先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔戴，等佢地瀨晒嘢後悔下先"},{"pid":"e82deb731241b90de883e37ff19045ec76d05505","tid":1835552,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>有冇人有興趣揾日一齊去飲啖茶食下姜</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊係坐爆成間舖頭，坐晚市三個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入嚟推post啦</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1833914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1833914</a><br />\n<br />\n可以留意下呢個Telegram頻道<br />\n希望大家集思廣益，打經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"3ab6063ff9948b6dc658637fdfbdabc5170273a9","tid":1835552,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3e83804351b501bbf720e28853c5d0c764fc04","tid":1835552,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e364093d513a669c235f5f1e9b9ebcc076178094","tid":1835552,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":